{"meta":{"title":"3 Nefi 30","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/30?lang=spa","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ/2017-11-2040-3-nephi-30-64k-spa.mp3?download=true","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"e7b3b0f99000f8fe8df61ba7a5c6a27c69973f30","data-aid":"124187831","data-aid-version":"3","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/30","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"spa","data-orig-id":"bb2b74eb6a2d2ae50f45b51e5fb078b84c3b0b41","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"3 Nefi 30","description":"Se manda a los gentiles de los últimos días arrepentirse, venir a Cristo y ser contados entre los de la casa de Israel. Aproximadamente 34–35 d.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"3 Nefi 30","description":"Se manda a los gentiles de los últimos días arrepentirse, venir a Cristo y ser contados entre los de la casa de Israel. Aproximadamente 34–35 d.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124187886\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 30</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124187887\" id=\"study_summary1\">Se manda a los gentiles de los últimos días arrepentirse, venir a Cristo y ser contados entre los de la casa de Israel. Aproximadamente 34–35 d.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124187888\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>¡Oíd, oh gentiles, y escuchad las palabras de Jesucristo, el Hijo del Dios viviente, las cuales él me ha <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>mandado</a> que hable concerniente a vosotros! Pues he aquí, él me manda escribir, diciendo:</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124187889\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>¡Tornaos, todos vosotros <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>gentiles</a>, de vuestros caminos de maldad; y <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>arrepentíos</a> de vuestras obras malas, de vuestras mentiras y engaños, y de vuestras <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"561\"></span>fornicaciones, y de vuestras abominaciones secretas, y vuestras idolatrías, y vuestros asesinatos, y vuestras supercherías sacerdotales, y vuestras envidias, y vuestras contiendas, y de todas vuestras iniquidades y abominaciones, y venid a mí, y sed bautizados en mi nombre para que recibáis la remisión de vuestros pecados, y seáis llenos del Espíritu Santo, para que seáis <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>contados</a> entre los de mi pueblo que son de la casa de Israel!</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"30\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124187890\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/5.12-13?lang=spa#p12\">3 Ne. 5:12–13</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124187893\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/gentiles?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Gentiles</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note2b\" data-full-marker=\"2b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124187895\" id=\"note2b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/repent-repentance?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Arrepentimiento, arrepentirse</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note2c\" data-full-marker=\"2c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124187897\" id=\"note2c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/gal/3.27-29?lang=spa#p27\">Gál. 3:27–29</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.18-19?lang=spa#p18\">2 Ne. 10:18–19</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/16.10-13?lang=spa#p10\">3 Ne. 16:10–13</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.22-25?lang=spa#p22\">21:22–25</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.10?lang=spa#p10\">Abr. 2:10</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note1a":{"id":"note1a","marker":"1a","pid":"124187888","context":"mandado","text":"<p data-aid=\"124187890\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/5.12-13?lang=spa#p12\">3 Ne. 5:12–13</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/5.12-13?lang=spa#p12","text":"3 Ne. 5:12–13"}]},"note2a":{"id":"note2a","marker":"2a","pid":"124187889","context":"gentiles","text":"<p data-aid=\"124187893\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/gentiles?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Gentiles</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/gentiles?lang=spa","text":"GEE Gentiles"}]},"note2b":{"id":"note2b","marker":"2b","pid":"124187889","context":"arrepentíos","text":"<p data-aid=\"124187895\" id=\"note2b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/repent-repentance?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Arrepentimiento, arrepentirse</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/repent-repentance?lang=spa","text":"GEE Arrepentimiento, arrepentirse"}]},"note2c":{"id":"note2c","marker":"2c","pid":"124187889","context":"contados","text":"<p data-aid=\"124187897\" id=\"note2c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/gal/3.27-29?lang=spa#p27\">Gál. 3:27–29</a>; <a class=\"s